commit.title: [gramlib] Pack gramlib in Makefile
commit.message:
[gramlib] Pack gramlib in Makefile

We use the style done in the packing of `Stdlib` in OCaml 4.07.

NB: if you run dune with display=verbose you can see it uses -w -49 to
compile gramlib.ml
